      "id": "1a76adc5_8b80d347",
      "file_path": "blueprints/k8s-datafile-collector.yaml-template",
      "patchset_number": 8,
      "line": 98,
      "message": "From the Data-Router documentation, https://onap.readthedocs.io/en/latest/submodules/dmaap/datarouter.git/docs/data-router/data-router.html\n\nPublish to Feed\n\nDescription: Publish a file to a created feed so that it can be shared to any subscribers of that feed\nRequest URL\n\nhttp[s]://{host}:{port}/publish/{feedId}/{fileName}\n\n    {feedId} is the id of the feed you are publishing to.\n    {fileId} is the id of the file you are publishing onto the feed.\n\nMaybe we shouldn't use the notion of a configurable topic at all, since \"publish\" is not actually configurable?",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 3763,
        "name": "Henrik Andersson",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "henrik.b.andersson@est.tech",
        "username": "elinuxhenrik"
      },
      "updated": "2018-09-26 10:36:20.000000000",
